It has a variety of features such as creating and sharing music playlists, discovering new music, and listening to popular and exclusive podcasts. It also has a Premium subscription option which allows users to download and listen offline, and access ad-free music. It is available on all devices and has a variety of genres and artists to choose from.
OUTPUT:
{"category": "App", "evidence": "Both"}
